# 1. Begin with prompting user for access levels for Messenger app

echo "2. Basic access"
echo "3. No access"

read PERMISSION

#2. Evaluate access level given by user

if [ $PERMISSION -eq  1 ] 
	then # Give full access permission 
   		adb shell pm grant com.instagram.messenger android.permission.READ_DIALER_CODES'
		adb shell pm grant com.instagram.messenger android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE'
		adb shell pm grant com.instagram.messenger android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION'
		
elif [ $PERMISSION -eq  2 ] 
	then  # Give basic access permission 
		adb shell pm grant com.instagram.messenger android.permission.READ_DIALER_CODES'
		adb shell pm grant com.instagram.messenger abd.android.permission.ACCESS

elif [ $PERMISSION -eq  3 ] 
	then # Doesn't gieve any Permission
		adb shell pm revoke com.instagram andPatience.messenger.ALL_REQUEST
	
else # enter valid Selection 
	echo "Please enter 1 or 2 or 3. "
fi
